pData(GSE111861)$day <- gsub("Tlr4 mutant_| .*","", pData(GSE111861)$title)
pData(GSE111861)$day[which(pData(GSE111861)$day=="vehicle_biological")]=0

pData(GSE111861)$Virus <- gsub("*_b.*", "", pData(GSE111861)$title)

Create matrix and DE

full_model <- model.matrix(~0 + Infection+Day, data = pData(GSE111861))
colnames(full_model) <- c("RSV", "Vehicle", "Day1", "Day5")
full_model

fit <- lmFit(GSE111861, full_model)
## Coefficients not estimable: Day5
## Warning: Partial NA coefficients for 12000 probe(s)
fit2 <- contrasts.fit(fit, makeContrasts(RSV - Vehicle, levels=full_model))
fit2 <- eBayes(fit2, trend = T)
de <- topTable(fit2, adjust.method="BH"

, number=Inf, sort.by = "P")

Volkano Plot

ggplot(de, aes(x=logFC, y=-log10(adj.P.Val), color=adj.P.Val < 0.05)) +

```r
topPathwaysUp <- fgseaResults[ES > 0, ][head(order(pval), n=5), pathway]
topPathwaysDown <- fgseaResults[ES < 0, ][head(order(pval), n=5), pathway]
topPathways <- c(topPathwaysUp, rev(topPathwaysDown))
```
